Some of John Nyagarama's supporters broke into tears as it dawned on them that their governor was no more.Interior Cabinet Secretary Dr Fred Matiang’i and Kisii Governor James Ongwae led Gusii elected leaders in receiving Mr Kenyatta. A sombre mood engulfed Nyamira County as reality of the passing of governor John Nyagarama sank on the residents on Wednesday.
An interdenominational prayer service was held at Nyamira Primary School grounds in the governor’s honour, setting the tone for the burial ceremony tomorrow.
Some of his supporters broke into tears as it dawned on them that their governor was no more. Before the Wednesday function, most of them had only heard on media that he had passed on about six days ago.



